lead_paragraph: Phillies third baseman Maikel Franco hit his major league-leading ninth homer of spring training, but Garabez Rosa hit a tying homer in the ninth inning for Baltimore and then another run scored on a wild pitch to give the Orioles an 8-7 win over Philadelphia on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Franco Homers Again, but Orioles Beat Phillies 8-7
